@startuml
skinparam dpi 150
actor 用户 as User

rectangle "任务队列 & 调度" {
  [任务队列 (Kafka)] as Queue
  [调度器 (Scheduler / Autoscaler)] as Scheduler
}

cloud "算力集群" as Cluster {
  node "算力组 A (并发复用/弹性伸缩)" as GroupA {
    node "算力子组 2" as SubgroupA2 {
      database "GPU 3\n(编码)" as GPU3
      database "GPU 4\n(k分片检索)" as GPU4
      database "GPU 5\n(k分片检索)" as GPU5
    }

    node "算力子组 1" as SubgroupA1 {
      database "GPU 0\n(编码)" as GPU0
      database "GPU 1\n(k分片检索)" as GPU1
      database "GPU 2\n(k分片检索)" as GPU2
    }
  }
  node "算力组 B (Replica/冷数据)" as GroupB {
    node "CPU 检索节点 (冷数据/低优先级)" as CPUIndex
  }
}

rectangle "数据库层" as DB {
  database "Redis 高速缓存" as Redis
  database "Postgres 元数据存储" as Postgres
}

rectangle "聚合 & 后处理" as Merge {
  [结果合并器 (k-way merge, heap)]
  [元数据拉取 & 响应构建]
}

User -> Queue : 请求 (query sequence)
Queue --> Scheduler : 拉取 & 调度
Scheduler --> GroupA : 分配到算力组

GPU0 --> GPU1 : Tensor转移(NVLink)
GPU0 --> GPU2 : Tensor转移(NVLink)
GPU3 --> GPU4 : Tensor转移(NVLink)
GPU3 --> GPU5 : Tensor转移(NVLink)

GPU1 --> Merge : 返回 id + score
GPU2 --> Merge
GPU4 --> Merge
GPU5 --> Merge

Merge --> Redis : 尝试命中缓存 (query->topIDs)
Redis <-- Postgres
Redis --> User : 返回结果

@enduml